With the Auda-Taller tool, the company Audatex guarantees that the user gets a budget in just four steps: identify the vehicle, look for the replacement, create budget and generate budget.
The ease of use is an essential condition for these systems, especially to convince older professionals, who are often more or less reluctant to use new management techniques.
